{"tid":1474880,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"楂住個春袋，唔好放手呀（多圖)","createTime":"2019-08-15T10:11:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-22T03:55:28.000Z","uid":296350,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"62da2eb15381b71a448b36fe1060ea39b476a485","tid":1474880,"uid":296350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:11:24.000Z","msg":"機場堅係春袋，唔好放棄！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">齋睇佢哋極速冚停就知<br />\n佢哋堅驚呀！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">Fact</span></span></strong><br />\n1. 星期二：公佈全部航班Cancel，實情又唔係<br />\n2. 星期一：現場不停亂放風話機鐵停駛，又吹清場<br />\n3. 連續三日入機場，機管局網頁聲稱1及4停車場Full，路牌寫Full，門口都寫Full、入面係有位架<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全撚部都係假嘅<br />\nOfficial公佈嘅消息都要做假<br />\n可想然知佢哋幾撚驚</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">只許持有效機票進入</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bUhr6j2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbUhr6j2.jpg&h=cff027bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/om2S1Tq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fom2S1Tq.jpg&h=17134eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7Sbc1Tt.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7Sbc1Tt.jpg&h=a22f65ab&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">接機只可在門外食塵</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kNtbx1c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkNtbx1c.jpg&h=7c74bed0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一日成功係因為<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">夠人</span></span></strong>成條路塞曬<br />\n佢運作唔到<br />\n如果我哋第一日嘅全部人<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">有車揸車<br />\n冇車搭巴士機鐵<br />\n</span></span></strong><br />\n癱瘓去機場嘅交通<br />\n佢一樣要停<br />\n絕對和理非又不損兵折將<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">抗爭成本低又舒服 <br />\n效果又大</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">夠人就塞交通<br />\n唔夠人都可以塞佢行人入口</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BKoi4Ji.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBKoi4Ji.jpg&h=3b72e203&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢個係其中一個入口<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">，幾百人搞掂！！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n需要大家支持<br />\n需要大量文宣配合<br />\n<br />\n你咪遊車河都出埋禁制令囉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一齊諗掂佢呀！！！"},{"pid":"684561e2cfc0d49c0895b568092b0f3121080e7f","tid":1474880,"uid":47222,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:18:57.000Z","msg":"推 快d搞返機場"},{"pid":"b64b986ca71ff0af74192cd232979649ad0885a3","tid":1474880,"uid":31762,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:20:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc754737fd87266d56c7580ca63e879ea19107b8","tid":1474880,"uid":29510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"點入去, 門口check 得好緊"},{"pid":"75e94e3f7a60c89ccd0dde4df2b18198bc7e5d7f","tid":1474880,"uid":296350,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"dc754737fd87266d56c7580ca63e879ea19107b8","tid":1474880,"uid":29510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:20:33.000Z","msg":"點入去, 門口check 得好緊"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T10:21:39.000Z","msg":"唔使入去<br />\n喺門口塞住<br />\n佢已經入唔到去"},{"pid":"403e4e0c2ea7ada185f9afac8e25ffa6dec81e71","tid":1474880,"uid":37135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"repl